00:13:01,485 --> 00:13:07,670
in God of War again, to bring in those absorption mechanics from that very raw documentary style

236
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:13,214
on top of that third-person camera to bring the relationship to the content from them

237
00:13:13,214 --> 00:13:21,221
to me. That way, instead of sympathizing with the character, we're empathizing as the character.

238
00:13:21,221 --> 00:13:26,845
So what was it in the documentary style we chose to latch onto from a visual standpoint?

