00:13:36,770 --> 00:13:42,514
Because we never hit the spoon with something that we are not used to seeing in real life.

243
00:13:42,514 --> 00:13:47,858
We also shot handheld style, which is something that we're used to seeing with our smartphones

244
00:13:47,858 --> 00:13:49,018
and our home videos.

245
00:13:49,018 --> 00:13:50,839
These are things that are realistic.

246
00:13:50,839 --> 00:13:52,961
This is stuff that we're used to seeing every day.

247
00:13:53,491 --> 00:13:57,492
Our shot design from a lighting and environment design standpoint was very naturalistic.

248
00:13:57,492 --> 00:14:02,793
We didn't go the whole soundstage Hollywood style where all the lights are painted and

